room_title: Escape room "The Mysterious Room" by Amaze Room Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: I've done 5 different escape rooms, 2 in Canada and 3 in NC and Amaze Room Escapes was the best escape room I've done so far in NC. The staff was incredibly helpful and had a good sense of humor. We had a group of 6 and did the mystery room. We're definitely coming back to try prison break!
